---

<Section sectionId="about">
  <div class="section__content flex justify-center">
    <div
      x-show="shown"
      class="invisible"
      x-bind:class="{ 'invisible': !shown }"
      x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-500"
      x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 transform translate-y-8"
      x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 transform translate-y-0"
      x-transition:leave="transition ease-in duration-500"
      x-transition:leave-start="opacity-100 transform translate-y-0"
      x-transition:leave-end="opacity-0 transform translate-y-8"
    >
      <h2>About the festival</h2>
      <p>Talks, workshops, games & music; a festival for DAOists and Regens.</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-16">
				<div class="relative">
        <div class="relative p-3 md:p-8 z-10 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-secondary to-secondary-dark-alpha-60 flex-col items-stretch h-full space-y-2 md:space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">An Unmissable Web3 Event</h3>
          <ul class="">
            <li>Ignite your passion for building a better future amidst global challenges</li>
            <li>Join a vibrant community of DAO enthusiasts and Web3 pioneers</li>
            <li>Experience a unique fusion of personal growth and revolutionary thinking</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
				<div class="absolute -inset-[1px] rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-accent to-transparent -z-10 pointer-events-none" />
			</div>
			<div class="relative">
        <div class="relative p-3 md:p-8 z-10 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-secondary to-secondary-dark-alpha-60 flex-col items-stretch h-full space-y-2 md:space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Empowering Topics & Workshops</h3>
          <ul class="">
            <li>Delve into cutting-edge decentralized organizing and DAO management</li>
            <li>Learn the latest Web3 and regeneration strategies from industry experts</li>
            <li>Enhance your work-life balance with creative workshops and meditation sessions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
				<div class="absolute -inset-[1px] rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-accent to-transparent -z-10 pointer-events-none" />
				</div>
				<div class="relative">
        <div class="relative p-3 md:p-8 z-10 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-secondary to-secondary-dark-alpha-60 flex-col items-stretch h-full space-y-2 md:space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Unforgettable Networking & Adventures</h3>
          <ul class="">
            <li>Forge lasting connections while exploring national parks and water parks</li>
            <li>Fuel your competitive side with adrenaline-pumping paintball battles</li>
            <li>Relish a spectacular week-long bus trip along the breathtaking Dubrovnik coast</li>
